"number\">0</span>; i &lt; hexString.<span class=\"property\">length</span>; i += <span class=\"number\">4</span>) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> hex = hexString.<span class=\"title function_\">substr</span>(i, <span class=\"number\">4</span>);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (hex.<span class=\"property\">length</span> === <span class=\"number\">4</span>) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> charCode = <span class=\"built_in\">parseInt</span>(hex, <span class=\"number\">16</span>);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!<span class=\"built_in\">isNaN</span>(charCode)) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                        decodedText += <span class=\"title class_\">String</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">fromCharCode</span>(charCode);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                    &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                        <span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">error</span>(<span class=\"string\">`Invalid hex code: <span class=\"subst\">$&#123;hex&#125;</span>`</span>);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                    &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">                &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">            &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">            <span class=\"variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">getElementById</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;result&#x27;</span>).<span class=\"property\">textContent</span> = decodedText;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">        &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-javascript\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>一个简单的文本编码器，采用了 UTF-16 编码原理用“啦咯噜咧”这四个字代替了十六进制数字</p>\n","isPage":false,"isDraft":false,"permalink":"http://example.com/2025/09/23/%E5%A4%96%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/"},{"title":"link","content":"","isPage":true,"isDraft":false,"permalink":"http://example.com/link/index.html"},{"title":"tags","content":"","isPage":true,"isDraft":false,"permalink":"http://example.com/tags/index.html"},{"title":"分类","content":"","isPage":true,"isDraft":false,"permalink":"http://example.com/categories/index.html"}]